      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without systematic evaluation of alternative closures. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power law used without assessment of model form uncertainty relative to modified power law or strain-based models. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
    {
