      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed for inlet flow and blood viscosity; hemolysis power law coefficients treated as fixed despite known inter-study variability of ±40%. Input characterization incomplete for MRL 5 absolute prediction. 95% prediction intervals span ±52% of mean NIH. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
